message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with image computing algorithms and deep learning networks for segmentation and error map prediction in medical imaging, specifically for whole-heart segmentation. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) domains. Additionally, the use case is in the medical field (cs.MED) and involves neural networks (cs.NEURON).
